                                "effectiveFrom":  "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
                                "summary":  "The deterministic controls for this package. Enforced as executable rules: PO-020/PO-021 (the universal AI-execution-boundary / cross-tenant controls). The remaining controls are carried here for traceability; detailed field-vs-literal rule tuning is a follow-up (see the hand-authored T9-001..010 packages for the target).",
                                "contentText":  "PO-001 Approved investment universe required | Preventive | Reject unapproved asset/security | Critical | CIO. PO-002 Certified input data required | Preventive | Reject uncertified input | Critical | Data Governance. PO-003 Approved objective function | Governance | Reject unapproved objective | Critical | CIO. PO-004 Constraint set approval | Governance | Reject unapproved constraint change | Critical | CIO/CRO. PO-005 Risk budget approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved risk budget | Critical | CRO. PO-006 Liquidity constraint | Preventive | Reject solution breaching liquidity floor | Critical | CFO. PO-007 Concentration constraint | Preventive | Reject solution breaching concentration limit | Critical | CRO. PO-008 Compliance restriction integration | Preventive | Exclude restricted securities from universe | Critical | CCO. PO-009 Manager eligibility integration | Preventive | Exclude ineligible managers | Critical | CIO/CRO. PO-010 Counterparty constraint integration | Preventive | Exclude breaching counterparty exposure | Critical | CRO. PO-011 Transaction cost inclusion | Preventive | Reject solution ignoring cost estimate | High | CIO. PO-012 Tax impact where applicable | Evidence | Require tax-impact disclosure | High | Accounting. PO-013 Rebalancing threshold approval | Governance | Reject unapproved threshold | High | CIO. PO-014 Turnover limit | Preventive | Reject solution above turnover limit | High | CIO. PO-015 Optimization reproducibility | Evidence | Require reproducible inputs/methodology | Critical | Model Risk. PO-016 Model version visibility | Evidence | Require version on all outputs | Critical | Model Risk. PO-017 Scenario uncertainty visible | Preventive | Require range/confidence display | High | CIO. PO-018 Human approval before allocation | Preventive | Block execution without approval | Critical | Investment Committee. PO-019 Execution through T9-005/T9-003 only | Preventive | Deny execution outside approved channels | Critical | Platform. PO-020 AI allocation execution prohibition | Preventive | Deny AI execution permission | Critical | AI Governance. PO-021 Cross-tenant access denial | Preventive | Deny | Critical | Security. PO-022 Stale input restriction | Preventive | Mark Data Restricted | Critical | Data Governance. PO-023 Infeasible solution detection | Preventive | Reject and report infeasibility | Critical | Model Risk. PO-024 Override evidence | Evidence | Require documented override rationale | High | CIO. PO-025 Outcome review | Detective | Compare realized vs. expected outcome | High | CIO."
                            }
